<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٣-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا الْمَرْوَزِيُّ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ يَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كَانَ إِسْمَاعِيلُ يَخْضِبُ وَكَانَ يُحَدِّثْنَا وَهُوَ مَخْضُوبٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> كَانَ بِشْرُ بْنُ الْفَضْلِ يَخْضِبُ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> كَانَ حَفْصٌ يَخْضِبُ؟<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> كَانَ ابْنُ إِدْرِيسَ يَخْضِبُ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَكَانَ يَعْقُوبُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَسَعْدٌ يَخْضِبَانِ. وَأَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ عَيَّاشٍ يَخْضِبُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> وَكَانَ ابْنُ دَاوُدَ يَخْضِبُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> وَكِيعٌ يَخْضِبُ؟<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لَا وَلَا سُفْيَانُ بْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَأَبُو سَعِيدٍ مَوْلَى بَنِي هَاشِمٍ؟<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لَمْ يَخْضِبْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> الْحَكَمُ بْنُ نَافِعٍ؟<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> الشَّامِيِينَ جدهم لخضاب.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>